text: 'Malobika Banerjee' is a Bengali actress. She acted in movies like Chorabali, Katmandu and Mister Bhaduri. She has also done Oriya movies such as Mate bohu kari Nei ja, Dele Dhara katha Sare. == Filmography == {| class="wikitable sortable" |- ! Year !! Film !!
